@{bg fill}@{fg shine} Notes @{fg text}@{bg back}

* Execute this Shell command to check which version you have: > version full System:Classes/DataTypes/picture.datatype

* 48-bit to 24-bit conversions result in quite dark images

@ENDNODE



@NODE "Installation"

@{bg fill}@{fg shine} Installation @{fg text}@{bg back}

Below are the instructions for doing the installation by hand.

1) Copy the file "Classes/DataTypes/cr2.datatype" to the directory "System:Classes/DataTypes/".

2) Copy the file "Devs/DataTypes/CR2" and its ".info" file to the directory "System:Devs/DataTypes/".

3) Activate the CR2 DataType by
     * double-clicking its icon or
     * by executing the Shell command "AddDataTypes System:Devs/DataTypes/cr2.datatype REFRESH" or
     * by rebooting your Amiga.

@ENDNODE



